text: Lady Rothschild may refer to: *Emma Louise von Rothschild (1844–1935), wife of Nathan Rothschild, 1st Baron Rothschild *Barbara Judith Hutchinson (1911–1989), first wife of Victor Rothschild, 3rd Baron Rothschild between 1933 and 1946 *Teresa Rothschild (1915–1996), second wife of Victor Rothschild, 3rd Baron Rothschild *Serena Rothschild (1935–2019), wife of Jacob Rothschild, 4th Baron Rothschild ==See also== *Baron Rothschild
title: Lady Rothschild
